TITLEDivorceSTARRING Sarah Jessica Parker, Thomas Haden Church, Molly ShannonGENREComedyRelease DateOctober 9Divorce sees the return of Sarah Jessica Parker to the small screen. Parker stars as Frances, a frustrated woman living in quiet rage as she is stuck in a marriage she can&rsquo;t see a way out of. She sums up the courage to ask for a divorce from her husband only to call it off when her husband kicks her out of the house. Frances represents many women in the suburban lifestyle who are stuck between a marriage they don&rsquo;t want and everything else they stand to lose if they get out. The show encapsulates the dark humour embedded in the reality of failing marriages. Star rating: 3.5/5